{"type": "article", "id": 24162, "title": "便携式桌子", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-21T07:00:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607115642dVAC9TXkeS38jaNf.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这把折叠桌是由日本的 Torafu 建筑为瑞士品牌 WOGG 而设计，它可以收成一个很薄的形状以方便挂在墙上或移动。桌子是用铝制的，呈“A”字型，看起来十分轻盈，使用了 WOGG 特别的可通电的材料，在内侧安装了 LED 灯，可以用来当工作桌。灰色的桌子搭配简洁干净的线条让它极具工业感，这也是 WOGG 这个品牌的特征。目前还没有上市。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115640tgJIHxVPQ5W1T42Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115640Ojtkah2VJKSnb9QY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.02564103\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115641ful0Hq7rspeQ4x3m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.05235043\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607115641qkJnIxh1N90ZEVoM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.05555556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}